So anything that's here. Once you've been introduced to awareness there's nothing outside of your visibility. Making sense on on all this or any questions? I think it's pretty easy for the people in the live gathering. And wow, you understand self liberation, you understand what they call the Buddha view. So we sort of have normalized that, but it is great that pretty much all of you are catching on to this kind of thing. 

So yeah, I think in terms of self liberation and familiarization, that's all I have to really share about it. It's a really catch-all because when your mind starts to play tricks on you, there's still wisdom lessons coming. Your software is still getting updated, regularly. It has these automatic updates when you've been introduced to the view. And we can trust that oh, you know, awareness is taking hold. When we have some kind of disempowering narrative, some kind of afflictive emotion, what they call these _kleshes_---we can trust to leave it alone.


